# web-dist/ is TRACKED (T42): the prebuilt browser bundle ships in the repo so
# `npm ci --omit=dev` + `git clone` delivers the web GUI to a node with no build
# step. scripts/release.sh runs `npm run build:web` in preflight so a stale
# bundle dirties the tree and fails the release (the staleness guard).
